    "The p-value from two-sided Wilcoxon signed-rank test (null hypothesis H 0: median difference is 0; versus alternative hypothesis H A: median difference is not 0) is displayed between boxes.",
    "SALMON 11) under the same three cases as mentioned earlier and compared their performance with AUTOSurv.",
    "For the case \"mRNA + miRNA + clinical\", we focus on the comparisons involving AUTOSurv [\"entangle\" strategy].",
    "The results are summarized in Fig. 2.",
